    <p> Earthquakes can be naturally caused or artificially caused</p>
    <p> Artificially caused earthquakes occur due to mining, fracking, and nuclear tests</p>
    <p> Natural earthquakes are primarily caused by geological faults, landslides, volcanic activity, and other seismic events</p>
